ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: 684 is a good introduction to several different topics and issues in therapy. I would recommend it for this reason, because it is an ideal overview for the first-semester clinical student.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: This course provided me with an introduction to the practice of psychotherapy, which will be useful for developing my clinical skills. The professor also emphasized methodology and empirically-supported treatment, which will be useful when thinking about my research.
